org.codice.ddf.broker.ui

Interface UndeliveredMessagesMBean

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    UndeliveredMessages

    public interface UndeliveredMessagesMBean
    Interface for the Undelivered Messages MBean. Allows exposing operations to perform on a message broker's queues or topics and is meant to abstract away the details of various broker's Mbean implementations.
